{"tid":2129252,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"業主叫價態度軟化 粉嶺帝庭軒兩房減價賣610萬","createTime":"2020-07-28T12:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T10:44:57.000Z","uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e707a9e09f858b3ec59eed6991afc561c2b8ba5","tid":2129252,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T12:54:33.000Z","msg":"疫市下業主叫價態度軟化。中原徐家倫表示，香港疫情持續嚴峻，部分業主見市況回落，願增加議價空間。粉嶺帝庭軒5座高層F室，實用面積469方呎，兩房間隔，叫價620萬港元，原先業主企硬不減，見近日疫情嚴重，為加快沽貨，議價後以610萬元易手，呎價13,006元。<br />\n<br />\n徐家倫表示，新買家為上車客，見單位間隔合用，遂積極還價洽購，即拍板入市。原業主於1999年9月以187萬元買入單位，持貨約21年，帳面獲利423萬元，單位期內升值226%。<br />\n<br />\n減10萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39a5c868a2e7fedc30fa73a37926ada693ace63","tid":2129252,"uid":324930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de3877b645ec887a24d8a6f4ca301e41b23f8e0e","tid":2129252,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減10萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n超, 咁你個買家又肯買<br />\n<br />\n咁咪係市場成交公平價囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6596bb1b59193400287eb144a733fb626d4e878","tid":2129252,"uid":51369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:40:37.000Z","msg":"依個價點解唔買對面逸峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d627c806c97dbc73236495a24fc5473f51cf2ac9","tid":2129252,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"哇屌 真係大劈價 走啊再唔走冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/